OL,3,CFinal plans unveiled for #9m
OL,4,Ctransformation of Grainger Market
OL,6,FFinal designs for the multi-million-
OL,7,Fpound regeneration of Newcastle's
OL,8,FGrainger Market have been revealed.
OL,10,FNew plans released by Newcastle City
OL,11,FCouncil showcase how the historic city
OL,12,Fcentre market will be transformed by
OL,13,Fthe project.
OL,15,FIt is hoped the #9m works will begin
OL,16,Fin the summer to be completed by April
OL,17,F2025 after being largely funded by
OL,18,Fcash from the Government's Levelling
OL,19,FUp Fund.
