OL,3,CFinal plans unveiled for #9m
OL,4,Ctransformation of Grainger Market
OL,6,FThe main focus of the project is to
OL,7,Frebuild the market's arcade area
OL,8,Ffollowing the recent restoration of
OL,9,Fthe barrelled glass roof. An array of
OL,10,Fother upgrades are also planned
OL,11,Fincluding refurbished toilets, better
OL,12,Fsignage and automatic sliding doors at
OL,13,Fevery entrance.
OL,15,FIt is hoped that the facelift will
OL,16,Fallow the market, which has been at
OL,17,Fthe heart of Newcastle since 1835, to
OL,18,F"rival the best European markets"
OL,19,Fwhile protecting its unique heritage
OL,20,Fand the wide collection of traditional
OL,21,Ftraders.
