OL,3,CFinal plans unveiled for #9m
OL,4,Ctransformation of Grainger Market
OL,6,FConcept images show the market arcade
OL,7,Fbeing used to stage a variety of
OL,8,Fcultural events and other activities
OL,9,Fincluding live music gigs, vinyl
OL,10,Frecord fairs, plays, and fashion shows.
OL,12,FThe Newcastle City Council could also
OL,13,Fintroduce longer hours meaning it
OL,14,Fcould open regularly on a Sunday and
OL,15,Fat night for special events.
OL,17,FThere are also plans to open up public
OL,18,Faccess to the old air raid shelters
OL,19,Funderneath the Grainger Market.
