OL,6,FCivic centre officials are due to go
OL,7,Fout to tender this week to find a
OL,8,Fcontractor to complete the work.
OL,10,FCllr Alex Hay, the council's cabinet
OL,11,Fmember responsible for city centre
OL,12,Fregeneration, said: "This has been a
OL,13,Ftruly inclusive process, where the
OL,14,Ftraders' opinions have been listened
OL,15,Fto throughout, and these designs have
OL,16,Fbeen shaped by them.
