OL,4,Ctransformation of Grainger Market
OL,6,F"We have a unique asset in the
OL,7,FGrainger Market, and it is more than
OL,8,Fjust a striking and historic building.
OL,9,FIt is a community that has been
OL,10,Fcreated over the years by loyal
OL,11,Ftraders and customers.
OL,13,F"They will continue to be as important
OL,14,Fas ever but to secure the market's
OL,15,Ffuture it must move forward and
OL,16,Fbroaden its appeal and customer base.
